doctype html
head
  meta(charset='utf-8')
  meta(name='x-apple-disable-message-reformatting')
  meta(http-equiv='x-ua-compatible' content='ie=edge')
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
  meta(name='format-detection' content='telephone=no, date=no, address=no, email=no')
  link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&display=swap' rel='stylesheet' media='screen')
  style.
    .title:hover * {
    text-decoration: underline;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width:600px) {
    table {
    font-size: 20px !important;
    width: 55rem !important;
    }
    }
div(style='display: block; background-color: #111827; padding: 2.5rem 0;')
  table(style='margin: 0 auto; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; color: #fff; font-size: 16px; width: 48rem;')
    tr
      td(style="text-align: center;" colspan='3')
        if applicationUrl
          a(href=applicationUrl style='margin: 0 1rem;')
            img(src=applicationUrl +'/jellyfin_full.png' style='width: 26rem; image-rendering: crisp-edges; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;')
        else
          div(style='margin: 0 1rem 2.5rem; font-size: 3em; font-weight: 700;')
            | #{applicationTitle}
    if recipientName !== recipientEmail
      tr
        td(style='text-align: center;' colspan='3')
          div(style='margin: 1rem 0 0; font-size: 1em;')
            | Hi, #{firstName}.
    tr
      td(style='text-align: center;' colspan='3')
        div(style='margin: 1rem 0 0; font-size: 1em;')
          | You now have access to Jellyfin and Jellyseerr as they sharing same account with the following credentials:
        div(style='margin: 1rem 0 0; font-size: 1em; font-weight: 500; line-height: 2.25em;')
          span(style='padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; border: 1px solid rgb(100,100,100); font-family: monospace;')
            | #{recipientName} | #{password}
    tr
      td(style='text-align: center;' colspan='3')
        div(style='margin: 1rem 0 2rem; font-size: 1em;' )
          | You can change your password at any time by visiting your account "Profile" directly in Jellyfin.
    if applicationUrl
      tr
        td(style='padding: 0px 20px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;')
          p(style='width: 23.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px;') You can request for movies, shows and music on Jellyseerr via the button below or ******.com
          img(src=applicationUrl +'/jellyseerr_preview_mobile.jpg' style='width: 26rem; image-rendering: crisp-edges; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;')
          a(href=applicationUrl style='display: block; margin: 0 auto; text-decoration: none; max-width: 200px;')
            span(style='padding: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(99,102,241); color: #fff; display: block; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);')
              | Open Jellyseerr

        td(style='width: 1px; background-color: #e5e7eb;')

        td(style='padding: 0px 20px; text-align: center; vertical-align: top;')
          p(style='width: 23.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px;') You can access your account and play media on Jellyfin via the button below or *****.com
           img(src=applicationUrl +'/jellyfin_preview_mobile.jpg' style='width: 26rem; image-rendering: crisp-edges; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;')
          a(href=applicationUrl style='display: block; margin: 0 auto; text-decoration: none; max-width: 200px;')
            span(style='padding: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(99,102,241); color: #fff; display: block; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);')
              | Open Jellyfin
    tr
      td(style='text-align: center;' colspan='3')
        div(style='margin: 3rem 0 0; font-size: 0.75em;')
          | Your account is strictly personal and should not be shared. Feel free to use it as much as you want within the same household, but be aware that any suspicious activity may result in a permanent ban.
